graph TB
    Input[Token IDs] --> Embed[Embedding Layer<br/>hidden=7168]
    Embed --> TransformerStack[Transformer Stack<br/>61 Layers]

    TransformerStack --> DenseBlock[Dense Block<br/>Layers 1-3]
    DenseBlock --> Norm1[Layer Normalization]
    Norm1 --> Attention1[Attention<br/>h=128, kv=128]
    Attention1 --> DenseFFN1[Dense FFN<br/>7168→18432→7168]
    DenseFFN1 --> MoeBlock[MoE Block<br/>Layers 4-61]

    MoeBlock --> Norm2[Layer Normalization]
    Norm2 --> Attention2[Attention<br/>h=128, kv=128]
    Attention2 --> MoeFFN[MoE FFN<br/>256 experts, 8/tok<br/>shared_expert + routed_experts]
    MoeFFN --> OutputNorm[Final RMSNorm<br/>7168]

    OutputNorm --> LMHead[LM Head<br/>7168→129280]
    LMHead --> Output[Logits]

    style TransformerStack fill:#f9f9f9,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Attention1 fill:#e1f5ff
    style Attention2 fill:#e1f5ff
    style DenseFFN1 fill:#fff4e1
    style MoeFFN fill:#ffe4e1
